ute. This is faster than ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Zero SH"]}, " but can cause issues for some external viewers after export."], "extent": [2610, 2765]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "sh_options"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Hue"], "extent": [2765, 2770], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Hue offset, in degrees, for the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["sh_coefficients"]}, "."], "extent": [2788, 2848]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "hue"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Saturation"], "extent": [2848, 2860], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Saturation multiplier for the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["sh_coefficients"]}, ". "], "extent": [2885, 2944]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [2944, 2953], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["It\u2019s sometimes useful to use a value of zero (desaturate) if you intend to boost the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Value"]}, "."], "extent": [2953, 3064]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "saturation"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Value"], "extent": [3064, 3071], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Value ramp (remap) for the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["sh_coefficients"]}, ". This can be used to reduce or enhance the view dependent effects. \n    For example, the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["smooth"]}, " preset for this ramp will effectively increase the contrast of view depdendent effects."], "extent": [3091, 3327]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "value"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [3327, 3336], "body": [{"level": 1, "id": "re